reen_Party_(United_States)" title="Green Party (United States)">United States</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/w/index.php?title=Partido_del_Sol&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Partido del Sol (page does not exist)">Uruguay</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/w/index.php?title=Movimiento_Verde_Ecologico_de_Venezuela&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Movimiento Verde Ecologico de Venezuela (page does not exist)">Venezuela</a></div>
