ty_of_England_and_Wales" title="Green Party of England and Wales">England and Wales</a> (<a href="/wiki/Wales_Green_Party" title="Wales Green Party">Wales</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Estonian_Greens" title="Estonian Greens">Estonia</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Green_League" title="Green League">Finland</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/The_Greens_(France)" title="The Greens (France)">France</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Green_Party_(Georgia)" title="Green Party (Georgia)">Georgia</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Alliance_%2790/The_Greens" title="Alliance '90/The Greens">Germany</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ecologist_Greens" title="Ecologist Greens">Greece</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/w/index.php?title=Z%C3%B6ld_Demokrat%C3%A1k&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Zöld Demokraták (page does not exist)">Hungary</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Green_Party_(Ireland)" title="Green Party (Ireland)">Ireland</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Federation_of_the_Greens" title="Federation of the Greens">Italy</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <i><a href="/wiki/Green_Party_of_Kosovo" title="Green Party of Kosovo">Kosovo</a></i><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Latvian_Green_Party" title="Latvian Green Party">Latvia</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/The_Greens_(Luxembourg)" title="The Greens (Luxembourg)">Luxembourg</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Democratic_Alternative_(Malta)" title="Democratic Alternative (Malta)">Malta</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <i><a href="/wiki/Partidul_Ecologist_Alian%C5%A3a_Verde_din_Moldova" title="Partidul Ecologis